item.description:
Source : https://cults3d.com/en/3d-model/game/6mm-epic-2nd-edtion-necron-raider

Id objet : 6mm-epic-2nd-edtion-necron-raider

Prix : 0 euros

Collections :

  • epic infanterie NEC Nécrons-tactiques

Collections pour tags :

  • epic infanterie NEC Nécrons-tactiques NONSUP

Description :

1
2
3
4
5

Necrons never had any official models for epic scale games... unless you are willing to use chaos androids. That's so weird consider how few unit they have in their army back then. But what if we do?

Here's my take on a "2nd ed" style epic necron warrior. It might have too many details for a 6mm infantry- fortunately that's what printers were for! You can even scaled it up as a simple mono-pose model.

Other unit such as immortal, flayers might get added later on. No scarabs for very obvious reason.
